        <div id="" class="process-texts">
          <p class="process-text split-mask">Lor, my client, put her final dot to her doubts when she aligned her professional path with her reason of being to a single word: create.</p>
          <p class="process-text split-mask">Nativo is the place where anykind of creations are born in a city that need more reasons to be more than just work all day. <br> San Andrés Tuxtla, MX.</p>
          <p class="process-text split-mask">The journey started by the initial creators of the planets: the natives. Their energy and motion to survive is something all artists can relate.</p>
          <div class="process-text">
            <p class="split-mask">We got close together to imagine Nativo from it’s initial personality to it’s final form: a place were creatives and news in the practice loss their judgements and fears, have fun and relax around creating their minds. <br>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="process-text split-mask">Nativo is that close friend to the people around to her community and a urban brand merch dropper. Relax, you just gotta be you.</p>
          <p class="process-text split-mask">Hey, the table is placed and you, like home.</p>
